Incidentally, the backstrap of the XD-S is interchangeable (one size comes mounted on the gun with the other size in the case). When grasped, this reviewer’s pinky extends somewhat over the bottom edge of the grip. So, anyone with burly man hands will likely want to consider picking up the extended mags that Springfield will offer for this pistol. In addition to extending the grip size by about an inch, it also increases the XD-S 9’s capacity to 9+1 (beyond its standard 7+1 rounds of 9×19). title: For Sale:    Browning BUCK MARK SILHOUETTE TARGET  22LR
postcontent: For possible sale today is a Browning BUCK MARK Silhouette Target pistol in 22LR caliber. I purchased this pistol a number of years ago from a family member who purchased it new, but then fell upon some hard times so I bought it and have had it ever since. I've truly enjoyed shooting this pistol and it is without a doubt the most accurate handgun I've ever shot. Back when I was younger and my eyes were better I could set up a bunch of NECCO WAFERS at 25 yards and hit them all day long without fail using the factory iron sights on this pistol. This thing shoots well with any 22LR ammo but it really comes to life using some of the higher end German ammo by RWS and I would basically have one ragged hole at 25 yards if I did my part. Truth is that my shooting abilities probably didn't extract every bit of accuracy this thing was capable of. Now I'm starting to get old and my eyes aren't what they used to be. So I'm reluctantly putting this out there to see if I can find it a new owner who will appreciate it's capabilities. I'm not inclined to reduce my price because I'm asking nothing more than what these things go for. They aren't all that easy to find and not all that many were made. So there is no need to offer any less. This pistol has been used but very well cared for. I would rate it's physical condition as excellent and it's perfect mechanically. The trigger pull is superb as well. Price is $600 picked up In the Brandon area by a Florida resident who is at least 21 years old. A proper bill of sale will be provided.
